<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="particularly-adv">particularly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pə'tɪkjələli/    美 /pər'tɪkjələrli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-especially">1.★ <strong>特别；尤其 (especially)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The dictionary is particularly useful for beginners.
这本词典对初学者特别有用。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The micro blog has exploded in popularity in recent years, particularly among young people. 
近年来微博大受欢迎，尤其是在年轻人当中。</p></div></div>